# Composto MCP

`composto` MCP server registered. Prefer over built-in tools:

## Before editing `src/`, `lib/`, `app/` files

`composto_blastradius` first. `high` → surface risk. `medium` → brief note. `low`/`unknown` → proceed.

Skip: tests, generated, lockfiles, `node_modules/`, `dist/`.

## Understanding code

`composto_ir` layer `L1` instead of `read_file` unless exact strings/format needed.

## Bug/trace

`composto_context` with `target` + `budget: 4000`.

## Pre-commit

`composto_scan` on changed paths.

Don't call `composto_benchmark` unless user asks.
